OL,3,CSunak to warn against 'over-
OL,4,Cmedicalising everyday worries' in
OL,5,Cwelfare speech
OL,7,FRishi Sunak is to call for an end to
OL,8,Fthe "sick note culture" and warn
OL,9,Fagainst "over-medicalising the
OL,10,Feveryday challenges and worries of
OL,11,Flife" in a major speech on welfare
OL,12,Freform.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister will say the focus
OL,15,Fmust shift to what work people might
OL,16,Fbe able to do, amid Government
OL,17,Fconcerns some are being unnecessarily
OL,18,Fwritten off as sick and "parked on
OL,19,Fwelfare".
