OL,7,FDisability equality charity Scope has
OL,8,Fsaid it would question whether Mr
OL,9,FSunak's announcements are being
OL,10,F"driven by bringing costs down rather
OL,11,Fthan how we support disabled people".
OL,13,FOn Friday, Mr Sunak ` in his vision
OL,14,Ffor a "new welfare settlement for
OL,15,FBritain" ` is expected to pledge not
OL,16,Fto dismiss or downplay illness, but to
OL,17,Fcall for a "more ambitious" approach
OL,18,Fto helping people back to work.
