OL,7,FHe is due to say: "We should see it as
OL,8,Fa sign of progress that people can
OL,9,Ftalk openly about mental health
OL,10,Fconditions in a way that only a few
OL,11,Fyears ago would've been unthinkable,
OL,12,Fand I will neverdismiss ordownplay
OL,13,Fthe illnesses people have.
