OL,7,F"But just as it would be wrong to
OL,8,Fdismiss this growing trend, so it
OL,9,Fwould be wrong merely to sit back and
OL,10,Faccept it because it's too hard; or
OL,11,Ftoo controversial; or for fear of
OL,12,Fcausing offence. Doing so, would let
OL,13,Fdown many of the people our welfare
OL,14,Fsystem was designed to help."
OL,16,FHe will say there is a "growing body
OL,17,Fof evidence that good work can
OL,18,Factually improve mental and physical
OL,19,Fhealth".
