OL,7,FMr Sunak will add: "We need to be more
OL,8,Fambitious about helping people back to
OL,9,Fwork and more honest about the risk of
OL,10,Fover-medicalising the everyday
OL,11,Fchallenges and worries of life."
OL,13,FThe Government said recent NHS data
OL,14,Fshowed almost 11 million fit notes
OL,15,Fwere issued last year, and said many
OL,16,Fare repeat fit notes "issued without
OL,17,Fany advice, resulting in a missed
OL,18,Fopportunity to help people get the
OL,19,Fappropriate support they may need to
OL,20,Fremain in work".
