OL,7,FMr Sunak is expected to announce a
OL,8,Freview of the fit note system,
OL,9,Fsuggesting specialist work and health
OL,10,Fprofessionals should be charged with
OL,11,Fresponsibility for issuing them
OL,12,Finstead of GPs.
OL,14,FResponses from healthcare
OL,15,Fprofessionals, employers and people
OL,16,Fwith lived experience will be sought
OL,17,Fin a call for evidence launched on
OL,18,FFriday.
