OL,7,FJames Taylor, Scope director of
OL,8,Fstrategy, said: "We've had decades of
OL,9,Fdisabled people being let down by
OL,10,Ffailing health and work assessments;
OL,11,Fand a broken welfare system designed
OL,12,Fto be far more stick than carrot.
OL,14,F"Much of the current record levels of
OL,15,Finactivity are because our public
OL,16,Fservices are crumbling, the quality of
OL,17,Fjobs is poor and the rate of poverty
OL,18,Famongst disabled households is
OL,19,Fgrowing."
